eone warp in on top of it and immediatly exploding.-Creating a large troop of Drones, and releasing them a couple of sectors away from someones base.-Blowing up someones planet as they beg you to stop.-Camping someones homebase while offline... with your turret monster.It just Keeps getting better as I play. At first you are trying to figure otu the mechanics of all the blcoks and how to accomplish what you want to to do. But as I go along I am coming up with really complex ideas and then, overtime testing them.Magnetic mines, Shotgun turrets and stop effect Lasers, oh my.You are sleeping on the next great game. All space games will be compared to this in the future."
